				</ukm:Metadata><Secondary><Schedules RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Schedule DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4" NumberOfProvisions="40" id="schedule-4" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Number>SCHEDULE 4</Number><TitleBlock><Title>Housing costs element for renters</Title></TitleBlock><ScheduleBody><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/part/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/part/2" NumberOfProvisions="4" id="schedule-4-part-2" RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2018-12-31"><Number><Strong>PART 2</Strong></Number><Title>  <Substitution ChangeId="key-d46c9c5dc43cb19b194693ee0d87b1a4-1583315020802" CommentaryRef="key-d46c9c5dc43cb19b194693ee0d87b1a4">Exception</Substitution>   to inclusion of housing costs element</Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2013-04-29"><Title>No housing costs element for 16 or 17 year old care leavers</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/4" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/4" id="schedule-4-paragraph-4"><Pnumber>4</Pnumber><P1para><Text>Section 11(1) of the Act (housing costs) does not apply to any renter who is 16 or 17 years old and is a care leaver.</Text></P1para></P1></P1group></Part></ScheduleBody></Schedule></Schedules></Secondary><Commentaries><Commentary id="key-d46c9c5dc43cb19b194693ee0d87b1a4" Type="F"><Para><Text>Word in Sch. 4 Pt. 2 heading substituted (31.12.2018) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/1129" id="rnb8sic5-d3e51090a1310" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2018" Number="1129" Title="The Universal Credit and Jobseekers Allowance (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2018">The Universal Credit and Jobseeker's Allowance (Miscellaneous Amendments) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/1129)</Citation>, <Ci